et">]</span></span></div>
<p>If the work to be done is <a href=3D"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/rect=
ilinear" class=3D"extiw" title=3D"wikt:rectilinear">rectilinear</a> motion =
of a body with constant <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mass" titl=
