<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading4"><h4 id=3D"Electric_motors_and_electro=
motive_generators">Electric motors and electromotive generators</h4><span c=
lass=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a h=
ref=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DPower-to-weight_ratio&a=
